name: __TypeKind
description: An enum describing what kind of type a given `__Type` is.

values.name: SCALAR
values.description: Indicates this type is a scalar.

values.name: OBJECT
values.description: Indicates this type is an object. `fields` and `interfaces` are valid fields.

values.name: INTERFACE
values.description: Indicates this type is an interface. `fields`, `interfaces`, and `possibleTypes` are valid fields.

values.name: UNION
values.description: Indicates this type is a union. `possibleTypes` is a valid field.

values.name: ENUM
values.description: Indicates this type is an enum. `enumValues` is a valid field.

values.name: INPUT_OBJECT
values.description: Indicates this type is an input object. `inputFields` is a valid field.

values.name: LIST
values.description: Indicates this type is a list. `ofType` is a valid field.

values.name: NON_NULL
values.description: Indicates this type is a non-null. `ofType` is a valid field.
